------ NAVIGATION

ctrl + space          content drawer
F10                   full screen
F                     focus to object
left mouse + alt      pivot (вращение вокруг объекта)
G                     game view
ctrl + B              place of the object on project structure 



------ OBJECT MANIPULATION

ctrl + D              duplicate object
alt + drag            duplicate object
shift + drag          lock camera while moving obj
end                   snap to floor



------- OTHER

Ctrl + L              Rotate Sun






